itemDescription: Member of the United Kingdom Parliament (1871-1945)

wikipedia_page.main: Robert Hunt Stapylton Dudley Lydston Newman, 1st Baron Mamhead (27 October 1871 – 2 November 1945), known as Sir Robert Newman, Bt, between 1892 and 1931, was a British politician.

response: * Robert Newman, 1st Baron Mamhead (1871–1945), British MP for Exeter, 1918–1931
